  "text": "that is, outside the unit circle. In fact, the unstable eigenvalue of the reduced-order model is larger than the unstable eigenvalue of the full model. Note that the general POD procedure does not automatically preserve stability properties during the model reduction process. Criteria for preserving stability properties are derived in [CITATION_1] .",
